law.history: Repealed 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 109, sec. 40, effective March 30, 1992. -- Amended 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 159, sec. 10, effective March 30, 1990. -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 296, sec. 14, effective July 15, 1986. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 384, sec. 95, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 346, sec. 9.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: License to conduct horse racing or engage in simulcasting or intertrack wagering as a receiving track.
